                 View Menu  Down arrow icon            Breadcrumbs   College of Nursing    Alumni    Give Now        Give Now  Our COVID-19 Response: Nurses will lead us through.  During the current crisis, subsequent waves, and for future pandemics and healthcare challenges, high quality, well prepared nurses will lead us through.  One of the keys to overcoming healthcare crises is preparing legions of nurses with a top-notch UIC College of Nursing education.  Your philanthropy is urgently needed to help our students and faculty succeed.  Thank you for choosing to support the UIC College of Nursing!      College of Nursing Priority Funds       College of Nursing Scholarship Fund   $          Dean's Faculty Catalyst Fund   $          Experiential Learning & Simulation Lab Fund   $          College of Nursing Annual Fund   $          Dean’s Innovation Fund   $            Give Now            Research and Academic Department Funds   College of Nursing Doctoral Student Research Fund  College of Nursing Biobehavioral Health Science Fund  College of Nursing Health Systems Science Fund  College of Nursing Women, Children, and Family Health Science Fund  UIC Tawani Foundation Matching of the Midwest Nursing History Research Center Fund  College of Nursing Research in Narcolepsy, Sleep and Health Research Fund    $        Funds for UIC Nursing Campuses Beyond Chicago   UIC Regional Nursing Scholarship Fund  Kellogg Family Peoria Nursing Scholarship Fund  Norma R. Kelly Peoria Nursing Scholarship Fund  Peoria Program Fund  Lynn Kustes Endowed Scholarship Fund  Quad Cities Program Fund  Quad Cities Legacy Fund in Memory of Jeanne A. Gittings  Rockford Regional Program Scholarship Fund  Springfield Program Scholarship Fund  Urbana Program Fund    $        Global Health Leadership Funds   Beverly J. McElmurry Scholarship Fund  Carrol A.M. Smith Global Health Current Use Fund  Chieko Onoda Endowed Scholarship Fund  Virginia M. Ohlson International Studies Endowment Fund    $             If you wish to donate to a College of Nursing fund...   If you wish to donate to a College of Nursing fund that is not listed on the online form, or if you wish to make a gift to support additional UIC-wide efforts, visit give.uic.edu .  If you wish to donate to a funds at UI Health’s Healthcare Delivery Fund, please visit this link .       Give By Mail   If you prefer to give by mail, please make your check payable to the “University of Illinois Foundation,” and in the memo please write “for benefit of UIC College of Nursing,” and mail to:  University of Illinois Foundation P.O. Box 734500 Chicago, IL 60673-4500       Making a major gift via stocks, estate, or trusts   Please contact Steven George , Assistant Dean for Advancement.  The University of Illinois Foundation is an independent Illinois not-for-profit corporation and the official fundraising and private gift-receiving agency for the University of Illinois. All gifts are tax deductible as allowed by law. EIN: 37-6006007.           For more info on giving, contact:  Steven George   Assistant Dean for Advancement    Phone: (312) 996-1736  Email: steveg@uic.edu             Alumni    Back to main content           Meet Our Alumni    Upcoming Events    Alumni Board    Alumni Mentor Program     Tips & Suggestions      Alumni Awards     List of Distinguished Alumni    List of Outstanding Achievement Awardees      REUNION    Vital Signs Magazine    Give to UIC Nursing     Faces of Philanthropy    IGNITE Priorities    Plan Your Gift     The Dean's Circle      Current Scholarship Recipients    Give Now      Update Your Information    Office of Advancement              College of Nursing  UI Health                        UIC's seven health sciences colleges and health care delivery enterprise.       Quick Links    Directory    Research    Our Faculty    Job Openings    Diversity & Inclusion    CollegeInsider      Major College Units    Department of Biobehavioral Health Science    Department of Health Systems 